Steps taken for project:
1.) Set up Ubuntu 20.04

2.) Made docker install script
	PATH: ~/Desktop/projectx/docker/docker_install.sh
	***make sure script has execute (chmod 744 docker_install.sh)***

3.) Run script to install Docker: 
	$ sudo install_docker.sh

4.) Test install by running hello world image:
	$ sudo docker run hello-world

5.) Installed NGINX:
    sudo apt update
    sudo apt install nginx

6.) Adjust Firewall: 
	sudo ufw app list (list app configs that ufw can work with)
	sudo ufw allow 'Nginx HTTP' (opens port 80 for traffic)
	systemctl status nginx (check if service is running)

7.) Install Node and NPM:
	sudo apt-get install nodejs npm

8.) Fix permissions with npm 

8.) Install Yarn using NPM:
	npm install -g yarn